# 📊 Market & Opportunity

## The Gap Rastrum Fills

**No product today unifies photo + audio + video + ecological evidence in a single UI with offline-first operation, Indigenous-language UX, and native export pipelines to GBIF, CONABIO SNIB, CONANP and INAH simultaneously.**

